    "2022; Kammoun et al.",
    "2023; 1eRASS J114447.6-430858; DETUID: em01_176132_020_ML00001_002_c010).",
    "The light curve (top right) is binned in individual eroday visits, while the spectrum (bottom right) is fitted with an absorbed power law.",
    "Note that both best-fit lines (light blue) are simple physical models aiming to guide the eye and do not intend to encompass all the potential detailed features present in the spectra.",
    "The background model is shown as black dotted lines in both figures."
